I got this app because I'm pregnant and married to a long haul trucker. I wanted to mess with my husband and  tell him we were having triplets. I'm not thrilled with the selection. Yall need to add more than just the one twin U/S and it would be  cool to have a selection of higher multiples as well.  Unless you're trying to be super sneaky and intend to lie to someone through the length of pregnancy it's really not worth the dollar... until you can give your partner a heart attack with a quintuplet U/S.

I was fooled by my ex girlfriend for 4 months into believing that I was the father of her child. She created a fake ultrasound on this very app. Apps like these should be banned from the internet. All they are good for is for encouraging pathological liars to validate their own made up stories. Anyone who uses these apps with intent to harm or to work against another being truly deserves every bit of bad karma they have coming for them. If you readers have any humanity left, don't fall for this crap
